   3.6 Types of Routers (4/5) 
  
     n   Note that they are all routers, but, because they     have     different responsibilities,     they are given     different
 names.    
     n   BGs use the     BG protocol (BGP)     for
 routing.   
     n   IGs use     IG protocol (IGP)     for routing.   
  
 

